                <p>The Atlas Endeavour platform is designed on an adaptive, transposable platform, which can be tailored for GVW’s of 3500kg – 7500kg. It can be configured in either 4x2, 6x2, 4x4 or 6x6 variants, dependent upon role requirements.</p>
                <p>The multi-function load platform allows for 4-12 forward facing seats. The modular design allows for variants to be individually tailored to client needs with generic or specific roles in mind.</p>
