                <p class="lead">The Endeavour is targeted at those users who depend on their vehicle, even in the harshest conditions in the world. </p>
                <p>It was initially developed for the expedition/extreme utility market and the vehicle prototype has been extensively developed and tested in some of the harshest environments and terrains on the planet.</p>
                <p>It has been tested for prolonged periods in an off-road environment including a repeated series of extreme off-road manoeuvres to determine stress points and limitations.</p>
                <ul>
